.. code:: console

   $ ult SECTION SIGN
   U+00A7 SECTION SIGN
   Text: §
   RFC-1345: SE
   X11 multi-key input sequences:
     <Multi_key> <s> <o>
     <Multi_key> <o> <s>
     <Multi_key> <S> <O>
     <Multi_key> <O> <S>
     <Multi_key> <s> <exclam>
     <Multi_key> <S> <exclam>
     <Multi_key> <Cyrillic_pe> <Cyrillic_a>
   Category: Po (Other_Punctuation)

   $ ult BACKSPACE
   U+0008 control character (C0)
   Aliases:
     BACKSPACE (control)
     BS (abbreviation)
   RFC-1345: BS
   Category: Cc (Control)

   $ ult U+2603
   U+2603 SNOWMAN
   Text: ☃
   Category: So (Other_Symbol)

